description: Redevelopment of Imperial House comprising the demolition of existing buildings and erection of buildings ranging from 3 to 16 storeys to provide 81 residential units (Use Class C3) and 815sqm of replacement office accommodation (Use Class B1) along with landscaped courtyard and provision of 87 basement car parking spaces, 5 motorcycle spaces and 166 cycle parking spaces, vehicular access from The Greenway and vehicle out onto Edgware Road with pedestrian access from Edgware Road
